	<p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0378b17"/><lb ed="T" n="0378b17"/><persName key="A002261">釋僧慧</persName>，姓皇甫，本<placeName key="CN0640424Z05AA">安定朝那</placeName>人。高士<persName key="A002976">謐</persName>之苗<lb ed="T" n="0378b18"/>裔，先人避難寓居<placeName key="CN0420602Z01AA">襄陽</placeName>，世為冠族。<persName key="A002261">慧</persName>少出<lb ed="T" n="0378b19"/>家，止<placeName key="CN0421087T04AA">荊州竹林寺</placeName>，事<persName key="A002848">曇順</persName>為師。順，<placeName key="CN0360402M01AA">廬山</placeName><persName key="A001204">慧<lb ed="T" n="0378b20"/>遠</persName>弟子，素有高譽。<persName key="A002261">慧</persName><ptr target="fn18"/>伏膺<ptr target="fn19"/>以後，專心義<lb ed="T" n="0378b21"/>學。至<date key="j18788461879211" from-iso="0432-01-02" to-iso="0433-01-01">年二十五</date>，能講《涅槃》、《法華》、《十住》、《淨名》、《雜<lb ed="T" n="0378b22"/>心》等。性強記，不煩都講，而文句辯<ptr target="fn20"/>折，宣暢<lb ed="T" n="0378b23"/>如流。又善《莊》《老》，為西學所師，與高士<placeName key="CN0411302Z03AA">南<lb ed="T" n="0378b24"/>陽</placeName><persName key="A002812">宗炳</persName>、<persName key="A002973">劉虬</persName>等，並皆友善。<persName key="A002812">炳</persName>每歎曰：「<placeName key="CN0650000E01AA">西</placeName><placeName key="CN0000000E01AA">夏</placeName>法<lb ed="T" n="0378b25"/>輪不絕，<ptr target="fn21"/>者其在<persName key="A002261">慧公</persName>乎！」<placeName key="CN0320503Z22AA">吳國</placeName><persName key="A002649">張暢</persName>經遊<placeName key="CN0650000E01AA">西<lb ed="T" n="0378b26"/>土</placeName>，迺造<persName key="A002261">慧</persName>而請交焉。<date from-iso="0479-05-30" to-iso="0485-02-17" key="j18961611898251">齊初</date>，刺為<placeName key="CN0421003Z08AA">荊州</placeName>僧主。<lb ed="T" n="0378b27"/>風韻<ptr target="fn22"/>秀然，協道匡世，補益之功，有譽遐邇。<lb ed="T" n="0378b28"/>年衰，常乘輿赴講。觀者號為「<persName key="A002261">禿頭官家</persName>」。與<lb ed="T" n="0378b29"/><persName key="A000298">玄暢</persName>同時，<ptr target="fn23"/>時謂「黑衣二傑」。<date key="j18985901898973" from-iso="0486-01-22" to-iso="0487-02-09">齊永明四年</date>卒，<lb ed="T" n="0378c01"/>春秋七十有九。</p><p>後有<persName key="A003071">釋慧敞</persName>者，亦志<ptr target="fn24"/>素貞<lb ed="T" n="0378c02"/>正，代<persName key="A002261">慧</persName>為僧主，續有功効焉。<ptr target="fn25"/><persName key="A002261">慧</persName>弟子<persName key="A003072">僧<lb ed="T" n="0378c03"/>岫</persName>，亦以學顯，力精致血疾而終。</p>
